high_descs: go to end of tub next to black table
pick up pink sponge from corner of tub
turn right, face tub with two purple rags
place pink sponge in between the purple rags in tub
turn left, go to black table
pick up pink sponge on black table
turn right, face tub with two purple rags
place pink sponge to the right of the purple rag on the right
anns.task_desc: place two pink sponges in tub

high_descs: Turn right, then face the black table to your left.
Take the soap from the tub by the table in front of you.
Turn right and face the tub to your left.
Place the soap in the tub in front of you.
Turn left and face the black table in front of you.
Take the soap from the black table in front of you.
Turn right and face the tub to your left.
Place the soap in the tub in front of you.
Move to the right edge of the small black table between the door and the bathtub.
Pick up the pink bar of soap against the wall to the rear of the candle from the bathtub.
Turn around and move to and face the center of the bathtub.
Place the bar of soap between the two purple rags in the bathtub.
Move to the small black table between the door and the bathtub.
Pick up the bar of soap between the green spray bottle and candle from the table.
Turn around and move to and face the center of the bathtub.
Place the bar of soap to the right of the rightmost purple rag in the bathtub.
anns.task_desc: Place two bars of soap in the bathtub.
